  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Concurrency
    This class implements the threads that will test the concurrency of the web service
    TestAutoConfiguration
    This class runs some tests in order to check the correctness of the auto-configuration module
    TestAutoPlacement
    This class runs some tests in order to check the correctness of the auto-placement module
    TestFirmatoFW
    This class runs some tests in order to check the correctness of the new firewall model

    This class runs some tests to collect some data about the performance of the tool

    This class runs some tests in order to check the correctness of the VerifooProxy class
